snippet.title: Best VGM 1174 - Romance of the Three Kingdoms V - Phoenix Orchid
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Saturn / Playstation / PSP
Romance of the Three Kingdoms V (1995)
Phoenix Orchid
Takayuki Hattori
